<item>
            <title>[HBASE-5856] byte &lt;-&gt; String is not consistent between HBaseAdmin and HRegionInfo</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/HBASE-5856</link>
                <project id="12310753" key="HBASE">HBase</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;In HBaseAdmin &lt;br/&gt;
  public void split(final String tableNameOrRegionName)&lt;br/&gt;
  throws IOException, InterruptedException &lt;/p&gt;
{
    split(Bytes.toBytes(tableNameOrRegionName));  // string -&amp;gt; byte 
  }
&lt;p&gt;In HRegionInfo&lt;br/&gt;
  this.regionNameStr = Bytes.toStringBinary(this.regionName);  // byte -&amp;gt; string&lt;br/&gt;
Should we use Bytes.toBytesBinary in HBaseAdmin &#65311;&lt;/p&gt;</description>
